@mik-laj What specific things do you need? 
`schema` part must be equals `aws`. Query parameters must cotanins extra parameters. For example:  `aws_access_key_id=AA&aws_secret_access_key=BB&CC=aws_account_id'.
You should also write what the default `con_id` is in hooks and operators for this platforms.

@feng-tao In the end this is part of this bigger issue:
https://jira.apache.org/jira/browse/AIRFLOW-3562

In the end this would solve the out of sync issue between gunicorn workers
